      "comment": "DISABLED \u2014 httpbin.org returned 503 (rate-limited from repeated test runs).\nThe hard probe (body\u0027s _value stays null after the property read) lives in C#\nHttpChannelTests and runs deterministically; this was the goal-layer smoke.\nRe-enable the steps below when the http suite is revisited.\n- get http https://httpbin.org/json, write to %response%\n- assert %response!status% equals 200\n- assert %response.slideshow.author% equals \u0022Yours Truly\u0022",
